Buying spot
Identify your altcoin -> start DCA into a position. Buy some now, leave $ to add on dips later. For extra security - withdraw your bags to a cold wallet (also makes you more 💎handed). Glorious bull market is upon us - don't fuck it up!

RT to spread awareness

Buying spot solves this and saves you from stress. You're less likely to puke the position in case it temporary nukes or there is FUD around it. And believe me, there will be a series of random -30%+ corrections, FUD etc along the way. Bull market will test you. 

4/5

Funding

On top of that you pay funding. It seems negligible to you in daily/weekly context but it adds up over the long run. During hot bullish trends funding can range from 10% to 60%+ annualized. Imagine paying that much. 

4/5 https://t.co/Yx8IQlYEuV

If you buy on margin, you can be right with the direction or even targets but you probably won't time it correctly. Bullmarkets are notoriously known for wild -30 to -50% multiple shakeouts. You sure you will be able to stomach that on margin? Doubt it. 

3/5

Spot vs. Margin

Especially important If you're new to this market

Nothing is 100% certain but chances are high this is going to be a bull market. So, whatever you buy now - will be probably in good profit a year from now. Only difference is how you buy it (spot/margin)
